data.text:
Tunisian President Habib Bourguiba, who is spending a period of rest in this northern resort of Salsomaggiore (a place for termal cures), commented very favourably on June 20, 1960 the decision of FLN to send to Paris a group of representatives to start talks with the French Government. PHOTO SHOWS: Bourguiba making the statement during a press conferenze. (AP-Photo/str/Renzo Crovini)

Captions are provided by our contributors.
